prompts.frontCover:
Minimalist 2D flat illustration for a greeting card. On a clean, solid cream background, two cartoon characters based on Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo are depicted in a humorous and sweet scene. Lao Lao is the focus, shown with a joyful, slightly mischievous expression, wearing her white dress. She is playfully attempting to steal a comically oversized birthday cupcake from Jordan, who is on the right. Jordan, wearing his outfit from the photo (minus the graduation regalia and any text), has a look of happy surprise and is holding the giant cupcake, which has a single glowing candle on top. Little hearts and musical notes float whimsically around them. The art style is defined by simple lines, flat color, and minimal shading, emphasizing their expressions and the lighthearted action.

In the center of the card, the text "Happy Birthday Lao Lao" is written in a beautiful, readable, elegant handwritten cursive script.
